This tool is used to download all linked pdf files on one page.
For me, it's convinient to download matirials from the course websites :)
================Usage================
configurate the following strings in pdfdownloader.py:
+ 'srcurl': source url for pdf list page,
+ 'baseurl': downloading base url
+ 'pkgname': package to store the downloaded files
===============Example===============
Download the materials of cs229:
srcurl = 'http://cs229.stanford.edu/materials.html'
baseurl = 'http://cs229.stanford.edu/'
pkgname = 'CS_229_Machine_Learning_Course_Materials'

Enjoy the tool :)